text: "If 6 Was 9" is a 1968 song by English band The Jimi Hendrix Experience. It was released from their second studio album Axis: Bold as Love and appeared on the soundtracks to Easy Rider in 1969 and Point Break in 1991. ==References== Category:1968 songs Category:Protest songs Category:Acid rock songs Category:Blues rock songs Category:Space rock songs Category:Jimi Hendrix songs Category:Tori Amos songs
